sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(EPP) 9002/TCP gRPC
    participant PrefillVLLM as Prefill vLLM<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant DecodeSidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant DecodeVLLM as Decode vLLM<br/>8200/TCP HTTP
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Optimized Baseline)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc routing<br/>gRPC/9002
    EPP-->>GW: Selected backend (scored)
    GW->>DecodeVLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    DecodeVLLM-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: Prefill/Decode Disaggregation
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc (prefill profile)<br/>gRPC/9002
    EPP-->>GW: Selected prefill backend
    GW->>PrefillVLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    PrefillVLLM->>DecodeVLLM: KV cache transfer<br/>NIXL/5600 RDMA/TCP
    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeVLLM: Coordinated decode<br/>HTTP/8200
    DecodeVLLM-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading (Startup)
    DecodeVLLM->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>DecodeVLLM: Model artifacts

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 4: Observability
    DecodeVLLM->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>OTLP gRPC/4317
    PrefillVLLM->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>OTLP gRPC/4317
    EPP->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>OTLP gRPC/4317
